# Project Structure Guide

- Main entry point: [App.tsx](mdc:App.tsx)
- All UI components: [components/](mdc:components/)
- Data and constants: [constants.ts](mdc:constants.ts)
- TypeScript types: [types.ts](mdc:types.ts)
- Test files: co-located with components, e.g. [components/DhikrScreen/StageLearn.test.tsx](mdc:components/DhikrScreen/StageLearn.test.tsx)
- Test setup: [setupTests.ts](mdc:setupTests.ts)
- Build and config: [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts), [package.json](mdc:package.json)
- Coverage reports: [coverage/](mdc:coverage/)
- Documentation: [README.md](mdc:README.md), [CHANGELOG.md](mdc:CHANGELOG.md)

The app is a React + TypeScript project with Vite, Tailwind, and full test coverage. All features are modular and follow best practices for maintainability and scalability.
